commit.message:
[IMP] Convert, Relicense, and Upgrade
* Convert to standard Docker image instead of Clouder
* Relicense to Apache 2
* Fix cert generation
* Add support for intermediate/root switch off
* Add env vars for config locations
* Separate the trusted certs from the cert store
* Add a docker-compose for full PKI
* Add db generation
